---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="關於八字研究所 | StarKami"
  description="八字研究所致力於傳承東方命理智慧，結合現代 AI 科技，為每個人提供專業、免費的八字命理分析服務。"
  activePage="about"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
    <div class="pattern-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="ambient-glow" style="width: 400px; height: 400px; background: var(--jade); top: -100px; right: -50px; opacity: 0.08;" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container" style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
      <span class="overline">關於我們</span>
      <h1 class="display-heading">關於八字研究所</h1>
      <p class="about-hero-desc">
        我們相信，流傳數千年的八字命理不應該只是少數人的專利。八字研究所的使命，是讓每個人都能輕鬆接觸這門古老的智慧，透過現代科技的力量，重新認識自己、理解人生。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-up">
        <span class="overline">核心理念</span>
        <h2>我們的四大堅持</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-4">
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon-wrap">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--jade)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H20v20H6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H20"/><path d="M8 7h6M8 11h8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>傳統智慧</h3>
          <p>忠於千年命理傳統，嚴謹考證天干地支、五行生剋、十神體系，確保每一個計算結果都經得起檢驗。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon-wrap">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--jade)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M12 2a4 4 0 0 1 4 4c0 1.95-1.4 3.58-3.25 3.93L12 10V8m0-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4c0 1.95 1.4 3.58 3.25 3.93L12 10"/><path d="M9 16h6M9 20h6M10 16v4M14 16v4"/><circle cx="12" cy="13" r="1"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>AI 科技</h3>
          <p>運用最新的人工智慧技術，將複雜的命盤資訊轉化為易懂的個人化解讀，讓命理知識不再艱澀難懂。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon-wrap">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--jade)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2 12h20M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>免費開放</h3>
          <p>所有排盤工具和學習資源完全免費開放。我們相信，讓更多人接觸命理智慧，能為社會帶來正面的影響。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card fade-up">
          <div class="card-icon-wrap">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--jade)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>專業深度</h3>
          <p>從基礎的四柱排盤到進階的大運分析，我們追求每一個功能的專業深度，讓初學者和專業人士都能受益。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team Spirit -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-team fade-up">
        <div class="about-team-content">
          <span class="overline">團隊精神</span>
          <h2>融合古今的命理探索者</h2>
          <p>八字研究所的團隊由命理愛好者與科技工作者共同組成。我們深知，命理不是迷信，而是一套系統化的人生觀察框架。透過嚴謹的學術態度和先進的技術手段，我們希望為這門古老的學問注入新的生命力。</p>
          <p>每一行程式碼、每一篇文章，都承載著我們對傳統文化的敬意和對現代使用者的關懷。我們不斷學習、不斷改進，只為給你帶來更好的命理體驗。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-team-visual">
          <div class="about-symbol-container">
            <svg class="about-yinyang" viewBox="0 0 200 200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
              <defs>
                <linearGradient id="yy-grad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="var(--jade)" />
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="var(--bronze)" />
                </linearGradient>
              </defs>
              <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="96" fill="none" stroke="url(#yy-grad)" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.3" />
              <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" fill="none" stroke="url(#yy-grad)" stroke-width="0.8" opacity="0.15" />
              <path d="M100 20 A80 80 0 0 1 100 180 A40 40 0 0 1 100 100 A40 40 0 0 0 100 20Z" fill="var(--jade)" opacity="0.12" />
              <path d="M100 20 A80 80 0 0 0 100 180 A40 40 0 0 0 100 100 A40 40 0 0 1 100 20Z" fill="var(--bronze)" opacity="0.08" />
              <circle cx="100" cy="60" r="8" fill="var(--bronze)" opacity="0.2" />
              <circle cx="100" cy="140" r="8" fill="var(--jade)" opacity="0.15" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header fade-up">
        <span class="overline">聯絡我們</span>
        <h2>有任何問題嗎？</h2>
        <p>無論是合作邀約、功能建議還是命理討論，我們都很樂意聽到你的聲音。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-contact fade-up">
        <div class="about-contact-card">
          <h3>電子郵件</h3>
          <p><a href="mailto:contact@starkami.com">contact@starkami.com</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-contact-card">
          <h3>網站</h3>
          <p><a href="https://starkami.com">starkami.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container fade-up">
      <h2>準備好探索你的命盤了嗎？</h2>
      <p>免費、即時、專業的八字排盤，只需三步即可完成。</p>
      <a href="/tools/chart-calculator" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">立即免費排盤</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: calc(var(--nav-height) + var(--topbar-height) + 3px + 4rem) 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--near-black), var(--dark-indigo));
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    color: #fff;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
  }

  .about-hero-desc {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .card-icon-wrap {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--jade-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .card:hover .card-icon-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--jade), var(--jade-dark));
  }

  .card:hover .card-icon-wrap svg {
    stroke: #fff;
  }

  .about-team {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-team-content h2 {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-team-content p {
    color: var(--slate);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .about-team-visual {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-symbol-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
  }

  .about-yinyang {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    animation: slowSpin 30s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes slowSpin {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  .about-contact {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-contact-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--surface-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .about-contact-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .about-contact-card a {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--jade);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-team {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    .about-team-visual {
      order: -1;
    }
    .about-symbol {
      font-size: 6rem;
    }
    .about-contact {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
